data.description: Wonderfully modified Del Webb home located in the fabulous Active Adult Community of Sun City. This home features a large Arizona Room which gives you space for that large flat screen tv or maybe your hobbies, or entertaining? This is a great all around room with lots of light and enjoyable space. Step saver kitchen and two bedrooms. Entry into the home brings you into the living room so there is useful space all around. Desert landscaping and fruit trees for enjoyment and ease of care. Don't miss out on this great home, it is perfect for your busy retirement lifestyle. Fresh int. paint and professionally cleaned.
